Adverse Events Log

Source: R/data.R
ADVERSE.Rd

Adverse Events Log data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(ADVERSE)

Format

A data frame with 3675 observations and 89 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNIGO, ADNI3, ADNI1, ADNI2, ADNI4

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 2, ..., 10806

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • AENUMBER numeric Adverse event number Range value: 1, ..., 34

  • AECHANGE character Is this event a: 1=New adverse event ; 2=Worsening condition or symptom present at screening/initial visit Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEPENUM numeric Initial Health Assessment Condition Number: Range value: 0, ..., 59

  • AECOMPOUND character Is this event part of a compound event? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHONSDT Event onset date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AEOUTCOME character Event outcome 1=Recovered/Resolved ; 2=Recovering/Resolving ; 3=Not recovered/Not resolved ; 4=Recovered/Resolved with sequelae ; 5=Fatal ; 6=Unknown Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHCSDT Event cease date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AEHDTHDT numeric Date of death Range value: 2017, ..., 2025

  • AEHDBRN character Was a brain autopsy performed? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHCHRON character Initial Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHSEVR character Initial Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELAD character Related to symptoms associated with the development of early stage AD or progression of AD 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELCM character Related to concomitant therapy 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELFLRBTBN character Related to Florbetaben tracer 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELFLRBPR character Related to Florbetapir tracer 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHIMG character Related to PET/MRI imaging procedure 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELTAU character Related to Flotaucipir tracer 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELNAV character Related to NAV-4694 tracer 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELMK character Related to MK-6240 tracer 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELPI character Related to PI-2620 tracer 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHLUMB character Related to lumbar puncture 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELCOVID character Related to COVID-19 illness 1=Definitely (Confirmed COVID-19 test) ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELPAN character Related to COVID-19 pandemic disruption 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AERELATESP character Related to other study procedure(s) 1=Definitely ; 2=Probably ; 3=Possibly ; 4=Unlikely ; 5=Not related Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEHCMEDS character Was treatment (medication) for AE required? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AESERIOUS character Was event serious at any time during the trial? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AESERDATE Date event became serious: Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AEDTSITE Date site became aware that the event is serious: Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • SAELIFE character Is this an SAE because event was life-threatening? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEHOSPIT character Is this an SAE because it lead to hospitalization? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEPROLONG character Is this an SAE because it lead to prolongation of hospitalization? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEDEATH character Is this an SAE because it lead to death? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAECONGEN character Is this an SAE because it lead to a congenital anomaly or birth defect? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEDISAB character Is this an SAE because it caused persistent or significant disability/incapacity? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • SAEOTHER character Is this an SAE because it lead to another medically important condition? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE1 character Is there a change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE1 Change 1. Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AESEV1 character Change 1: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON1 character Change 1: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE2 character Is there a 2nd change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE2 Change 2. Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AESEV2 character Change 2: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON2 character Change 2: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE3 character Is there a 3rd change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE3 Change 3. Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AESEV3 character Change 3: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON3 character Change 3: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE4 character Is there a 4th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE4 Change 4. Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • AESEV4 character Change 4: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON4 character Change 4: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE5 character Is there a 5th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE5 logical Change 5. Date A Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV5 character Change 5: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON5 character Change 5: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE6 character Is there a 6th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE6 logical Change 6. Date A Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV6 character Change 6: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON6 character Change 6: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE7 character Is there a 7th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE7 logical Change 7. Date A Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV7 character Change 7: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON7 character Change 7: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE8 character Is there a 8th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE8 logical Change 8. Date A Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV8 character Change 8: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON8 character Change 8: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE9 character Is there a 9th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE9 logical Change 9. Date A Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV9 character Change 9: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON9 character Change 9: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHANGE10 character Is there a 10th change to report? 0=No ; 1=Yes Decoded Value: Yes

  • AEDATE10 logical Change 10. Date A Boolean value: TRUE/ FALSE

  • AESEV10 character Change 10: Severity 1=Mild ; 2=Moderate ; 3=Severe Decoded Value: Yes

  • AECHRON10 character Change 10: Chronicity 1=Single occurrence ; 2=Intermittent - daily ; 3=Intermittent - weekly ; 4=Intermittent - monthly or less frequently ; 5=Persistent Decoded Value: Yes

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 563, ..., 186890

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 1, ..., 941

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • DD_CRF_VERSION_LABEL character CRF Version Label , with options: v1

  • LANGUAGE_CODE character Language Code e=English Decoded Value: Yes

  • HAS_QC_ERROR character Has Quality Check Error 0=Does not have QC error or QC error has been approved ; 1=Has QC error Decoded Value: Yes

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
